; Pure MongoDB query/update semantics over Bson: selector matching (incl. geo, $regex, bitwise),
; update modifiers, projection, sort, document diffing (+ LCS for ordered observe), and id
; generation. Used by Minimongo and (later) the native Live engine. Pure OCaml — `re` is the only
; dependency beyond Bson and is itself pure, so the library still cross-compiles to JavaScript.
; Inline tests live in ../test.

(library
 (name query)
 (public_name fennec-mongo.query)
 (libraries bson re))
